{"data":[{"date":"09:14 03/08","title":"Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus: \"\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/3/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Leonardo Bonucci tin r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Milan.</h2><h2>Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Bonucci \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Turin v\u00e0o h\u00f4m qua trong m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Bonucci trong khi Mattia Caldara chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi San Siro thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGonzalo Higuain c\u0169ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Milan t\u1eeb Juve theo m\u1ed9t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Higuain c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n quay l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Bonucci kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean trang nh\u1ea5t. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u Juventini kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tha th\u1ee9 cho s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Bonucci c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp trung la \u00f3 khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1edbi trung t\u00e2m t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n<h2>Bonucci ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf v\u1ec1\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Bonucci-tro-ve-Juventus-Day-la-nha-cua-toi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus ch\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m sau khi r\u1eddi Turin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Bonucci kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m m\u00e0 anh d\u00e0nh cho Juventus v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t di\u1ec7u khi n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra\u201d, Bonucci chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean k\u00eanh Youtube ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c. Turin l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 Juventus c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Serie A v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Chievo v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 18/8. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Higuain, Caldara v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi \u1edf Milan s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Genoa t\u1ea1i San Siro sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, Juventus \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A th\u1ee9 8 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng si\u00eau sao c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Allegri c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Juventus:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bayern-munich-mia-mai-juventus-phi-tien-vi-ong-gia-ronaldo-176-192582.html\">Bayern Munich m\u1ec9a mai Juventus ph\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u00ec \u201c\u00f4ng gi\u00e0\u201d Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/sieu-sao-ronaldo-giup-juventus-pha-ky-luc-tren-youtube-188-192551.html\">Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo gi\u00fap Juventus ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c tr\u00ean YouTube</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5021","checkdouble":"192614"},{"date":"10:18 03/08","title":"Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/3/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i khi th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0110T U16 Iraq b\u1ecb ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng tham gia nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tra. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/dt-olympic-iraq-rut-khoi-asiad-2018-dt-olympic-viet-nam-bi-anh-huong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBan t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ASIAD 2018 (\u1ee6y ban Olympic Indonesia - INASGOC) ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Citizen, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a INASGOC x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u0103n b\u1ea3n xin r\u00fat lui c\u1ee7a \u1ee6y ban Olympic Iraq. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ASIAD s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i n\u00e0o n\u1eefa. INASGOC v\u00e0 AFC \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c thay \u0111\u1ed5i?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia c\u0169ng b\u00e1c b\u1ecf th\u00f4ng tin Philippines s\u1ebd th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Iraq. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hai b\u1ea3ng 5 \u0111\u1ed9i, m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng 3 \u0111\u1ed9i. B\u1ea3ng C ASIAD 2018 sau s\u1ef1 r\u00fat lui c\u1ee7a Iraq s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Syria v\u00e0 Timor Leste.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u 3 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Ngo\u00e0i hai \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 nh\u00ec m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng, b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba \u1edf c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 khi x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 4 v\u00e0 5 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o &quot;c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng&quot; cho \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, thay v\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ee7i ro theo c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-se-doi-dau-palestine-bang-doi-hinh-nao-168-192601.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Palestine b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-duoc-hua-thuong-tien-ty-cho-tam-hcv-asiad-168-192593.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee9a th\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec1n t\u1ef7 cho t\u1ea5m HCV ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-cac-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192577.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-lai-tung-hoa-mu-de-tranh-su-theo-doi-cua-cac-doi-thu-tai-asiad-168-192575.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ea1i tung h\u1ecfa m\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh s\u1ef1 theo d\u00f5i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-iraq-phu-nhan-viec-rut-dt-olympic-iraq-khoi-asiad-2018-168-192566.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-khong-danh-gia-cao-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-192541.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5020","checkdouble":"192622"},{"date":"09:06 03/08","title":"\u0110T Argentina c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi thay Sampaoli","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/3/dt-argentina-co-hlv-moi-thay-sampaoli.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lionel Messi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0110TQG hay kh\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n Lionel Scaloni. \u0110T Argentina c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi thay Sampaoli v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 40 tu\u1ed5i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Argentina sa th\u1ea3i Sampaoli</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf World Cup 2018 song \u0110T Argentina \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. Sau khi ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a HLV Jorge Sampaoli t\u1ea1i Argentina trong th\u1eddi gian n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ngay sau tr\u1eadn thua t\u1ee7i h\u1ed5 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tin chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Argentina c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi thay Sampaoli l\u00e0 Scaloni h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Argentina c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi thay Sampaoli l\u00e0 Scaloni h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/DT-Argentina-co-HLV-moi-thay-Sampaoli-la-Scaloni-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sampaoli b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, Sampaoli c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c bi th\u1ea3m \u0111\u00f3. Gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7 v\u1eeba qua, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina (AFA) \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng 2 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la M\u1ef9 cho HLV 58 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Scaloni l\u00ean t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, AFA x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0110T Argentina c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi thay Sampaoli \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Lionel Scaloni. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 40 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sampaoli t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Pablo Aimar, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t danh th\u1ee7 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft La Albiceleste.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lionel Scaloni\" title=\"HLV Lionel Scaloni\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/dt-argentina-co-hlv-moi-thay-sampaoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T Argentina c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi thay Sampaoli l\u00e0 Scaloni</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAFA xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, sau cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u1ee7a ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o, Lionel Scaloni s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110T Argentina c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Pablo Aimar v\u00e0 Mart\u00edn Tocalli\u201d, AFA ra m\u1ed9t v\u0103n b\u1ea3n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi Scaloni v\u00e0 Aimar\u201d, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch AFA, Claudio Tapia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi, \u0110T Argentina s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung. H\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Guatemala v\u00e0 Colombia \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bu-nhin-cua-messi-tai-argentina-chinh-thuc-bi-bay-ghe-421-191266.html\">B\u00f9 nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a Messi t\u1ea1i Argentina ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb bay gh\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-can-quen-di-tran-thang-argentina-421-190486.html\">Maradona x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 v\u00ec Argentina, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-argentina-tu-ung-cu-vao-ghe-nong-thay-sampaoli-469-190456.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Argentina t\u1ef1 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng thay Sampaoli</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5019","checkdouble":"192612"},{"date":"09:34 03/08","title":"\u0110\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Barca s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Arturo Vidal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/barcelona-dat-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-arturo-vidal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barcelona s\u1eafp ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Arturo Vidal t\u1eeb Bayern Munich khi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ed1t xong m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barcelona \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Arturo Vidal<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Guardian \u0111\u01b0a tin, Barcelona \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Arturo Vidal khi ch\u1ed1t xong c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Barca c\u0169ng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi ph\u00eda Bayern Munich v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf con s\u1ed1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barcelona \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Arturo Vidal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barcelona \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Arturo Vidal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/barcelona-dat-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-arturo-vidal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Barcelona \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Arturo Vidal.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nArturo Vidal d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Catalonia \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Barca. N\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t, Vidal s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Barca trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau Malcom (41 tri\u1ec7u euro), Clement Lenglet (35.9) v\u00e0 Arthur Melo (31).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Arturo Vidal nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Barca t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a Paris Saint Germain. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Barca c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Moussa Wague. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 19 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u Phi tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Paulinho<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ebfn Barca, Paulinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Guangzhou Evergrande. Vidal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Paulinho \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn Barca.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arturo Vidal gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich t\u1eeb Juventus n\u0103m 2015 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 32 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong ba m\u00f9a kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \"h\u00f9m x\u00e1m\", Vidal \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 22 b\u00e0n sau 132 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1edd phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Barca h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi-187-192602.html\">Barca s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gia World Cup trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thu-mon-barcelona-tham-vong-qua-mat-ca-messi-180-192583.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Barcelona tham v\u1ecdng qua m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ter-stegen-phat-bieu-ve-real-180-192570.html\">Sao Barca b\u1ed7ng d\u01b0ng \u201cn\u1ed1i gi\u00e1o cho gi\u1eb7c\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hlv-di-francesco-phat-bieu-ve-vu-roma-mua-hut-malcom-176-192485.html\">HLV Roma c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi khi nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi c\u00e1i t\u00ean Malcom</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/lionel-messi-va-dong-doi-lang-le-ve-hoi-quan-o-barcelona-188-192480.html\">Lionel Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eb7ng l\u1ebd v\u1ec1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u1edf Barcelona</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-khen-ngoi-malcom-180-192474.html\">Valverde \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean t\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5018","checkdouble":"192611"},{"date":"10:16 03/08","title":"Man City 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/7/4/man-city-80-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-psg-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti c\u1ee7a PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mahrez t\u1eeb Leicester, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Chi-80-trieu-euro,-Man-City-muon-mua-Marco-Verratti-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thay David Silva</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/choang-vang-voi-so-tien-man-city-dung-de-mua-isco-180-182894.html\" target=\"_blank\">Isco c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man City</span>, song HLV Lopetegui quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Real v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal, Toni Kroos c\u1ee7a Real Madrid hay Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Verratti c\u1ee7a PSG.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Verratti</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti c\u1ee7a PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, \u00f4ng coi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/Chi-80-trieu-euro,-Man-City-muon-mua-Marco-Verratti-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marco Verratti</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Verratti l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a PSG, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi PSG \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i anh su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barca, song th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 PSG y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Man City ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro. H\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn PSG nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5017","checkdouble":"192620"},{"date":"11:15 03/08","title":"Bayern Munich ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u00e1n Jerome Boateng cho MU n\u1ebfu....","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/boateng.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mua Jerome Boateng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, theo Daily Mail Bayern Munich ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu thu \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U quan t\u00e2m Jerome Boateng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Jerome Boateng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu chi \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mua Jerome Boateng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu chi \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/MU-mua-Jerome-Boateng-thanh-cong-neu-chi-du-50-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jerome Boateng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, anh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Boateng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man City \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao c\u00f9ng th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng, Boateng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-van-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-boateng-172-192293.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Boateng</span>, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern b\u00e1n Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mua Jerome Boateng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, theo Daily Mail Bayern Munich ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu thu \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <h3><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern chi ban Boateng voi gia 50 trieu bang\" title=\"Bayern ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/boateng.jpg\"></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, M.U ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ef1u sao Man City, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMirror cho r\u1eb1ng M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng Anthony Martial \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2u Boateng, song Bayern Munich kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t thay v\u00ec trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Bayern, M.U s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Yerry Mina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5016","checkdouble":"192625"},{"date":"10:58 03/08","title":"Aubameyang s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/aubameyang-se-dan-dat-arsenal-toi-nhung-danh-hieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nwankwo Kanu tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Aubameyang s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal, n\u1ebfu anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAubameyang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Emirates v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 10 b\u00e0n sau 13 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u2013 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ec3n sang Premier League. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 2, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Aubameyang, khi anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Kanu cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cN\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Aubameyang r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Aubameyang. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aubameyang s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Aubameyang s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Aubameyang-se-dem-den-danh-hieu-cho-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aubameyang s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Arsenal c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Arsenal: \u201cCh\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i cho Emery th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn, nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, khi b\u1ea1n tham gia v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf nh\u1eefng CLB l\u1edbn\u201d \u2013 Kanu k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aubameyang s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n Lacazette \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca-172-192623.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/21/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca-172-192623.html\">Arsenal c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Barca</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin Ousmane Dembele gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-arsenal-niem-tin-tu-nhung-lan-gio-moi-172-192569.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/goc-arsenal-niem-tin-tu-nhung-lan-gio-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-arsenal-niem-tin-tu-nhung-lan-gio-moi-172-192569.html\">G\u00f3c Arsenal: Ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\n5 ch\u1eef k\u00fd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Unai Emery \u0111em v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5015","checkdouble":"192626"},{"date":"11:11 03/08","title":"Cech mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 40 tu\u1ed5i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/cech-muon-thi-dau-den-nam-40-tuoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>36 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Petr Cech mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 40 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Edwin Van Der Sar trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nCech kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft th\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Cech \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 Arsenal, khi\u1ebfn CLB ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 v\u00e0 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Unai Emery, c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong th\u1eddi gian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang, gi\u00fap Arsenal h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Chelsea. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam m\u1ed1i nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Bernd Leno, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u00e0nh cho Petr Cech m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1edbn cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Cech cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. V\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 20 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i suy ngh\u0129 khi luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. V\u00e2ng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 Van Der Sar, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong 2-3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petr Cech mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 40 tu\u1ed5i\" title=\"Cech\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/cech-muon-thi-dau-den-nam-40-tuoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Petr Cech mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 40 tu\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft 100% nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. N\u1ebfu trong v\u00f2ng 6 th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 t\u00f4i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Leno &ndash; m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd pressing t\u1ea7m cao c\u1ee7a Unai Emery. Nh\u01b0ng Cech cho th\u1ea5y anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ngay c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn ph\u00eda sau, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1edbm \u0111em v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Leno, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Petr Cech mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 40 tu\u1ed5i, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/aubameyang-se-dan-dat-arsenal-toi-nhung-danh-hieu-172-192626.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/aubameyang-se-dan-dat-arsenal-toi-nhung-danh-hieu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/aubameyang-se-dan-dat-arsenal-toi-nhung-danh-hieu-172-192626.html\">Aubameyang s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nwankwo Kanu tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Aubameyang s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal, n\u1ebfu anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca-172-192623.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/21/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca-172-192623.html\">Arsenal c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Barca</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin Ousmane Dembele gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-arsenal-niem-tin-tu-nhung-lan-gio-moi-172-192569.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/goc-arsenal-niem-tin-tu-nhung-lan-gio-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-arsenal-niem-tin-tu-nhung-lan-gio-moi-172-192569.html\">G\u00f3c Arsenal: Ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\n5 ch\u1eef k\u00fd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Unai Emery \u0111em v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5014","checkdouble":"192627"},{"date":"11:25 03/08","title":"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Sao tr\u1ebb gh\u00e9t b\u1ecb cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/quan-diem-andreas-pereira-xung-dang-co-mat-trong-doi-hinh-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Andreas Pereira x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19 v\u00e0 \u0111ang chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pereira mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Andreas Pereira \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Granada v\u00e0 Valencia. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u00e3 thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00f3. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, ngay sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pereira \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i su\u00f4ng, Pereira \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U. Trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, anh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1eddi s\u00e2n mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t. Pereira \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u01b0a th\u00edch nh\u1eefng pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a n\u00f3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andreas Pereira x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Andreas Pereira x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/quan-diem-andreas-pereira-xung-dang-co-mat-trong-doi-hinh-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pereira l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 cong v\u00fat c\u1ee7a Pereira kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Liverpool c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 n\u00e0o trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup. Ng\u00e0y 29/7 \u0111\u00f3, M.U th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi 1-4 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 c\u1ee7a Pereira. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00ecn t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh t\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn thu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1p ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 n\u00f3i ri\u00eang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool, Pereira \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea7y cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t. C\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi anh ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. T\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u00e0y mai \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0ng trai 22 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n su\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Pereira c\u0169ng t\u1eebng ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i M.U. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi m\u1eddi c\u00f3 Valencia, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m. H\u1ebft h\u1ea1n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 b\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ed1c Brazil tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng chinh ph\u1ee5c s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andreas Pereira tai Valencia\" title=\"Andreas Pereira tai Valencia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Andreas-Pereira-tai-Valencia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>X\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAndreas Pereira x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U. Anh cung c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Paul Pogba, Nemanja Matic, Scott McTominay, Marouane Fellaini v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Fred, nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Pereira c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Ander Herrera cung c\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa cho M.U. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean c\u01a1. H\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Premier League, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eed th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andreas Pereira M.U vs Liverpool\" title=\"Andreas Pereira M.U vs Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Andreas-Pereira-M.U-vs-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pereira x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, M.U r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n s\u00e1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t ch\u1ebft ch\u00f3c nh\u01b0 Pereira. &ldquo;<em>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 6</em>&rdquo;, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 U23 Brazil n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>Mourinho \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn ra \u1edf t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 s\u1ed1 6 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh khi ra s\u00e2n</em>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sau-nhieu-nam-tu-nghiep-sao-tre-duoc-mourinho-trao-co-hoi-172-192616.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/sau-nhieu-nam-tu-nghiep-sao-tre-duoc-mourinho-trao-co-hoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sau-nhieu-nam-tu-nghiep-sao-tre-duoc-mourinho-trao-co-hoi-172-192616.html\">Sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m tu nghi\u1ec7p, sao tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</span><br>\r\n<span>B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, HLV Jose Mourinho trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Andreas Pereira \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Valencia.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Mourinho c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Pereira \u1edf m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00edch nghi nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong vai tr\u00f2 s\u1ed1 6, Pereira h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i M.U. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, song k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Matic c\u00f9ng Pogba chi\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u00edt nh\u1ea5t trong m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng Pereira ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f9ng Fred. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho va Andreas Pereira\" title=\"Mourinho va Andreas Pereira\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Mourinho-va-Andreas-Pereira.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin \u1edf HLV&nbsp;Mourinho</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Pereira hay Herrera s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 sung s\u1ef1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1ea3 Matic, Fred hay Pogba c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. 2 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Granada v\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Pereira tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. Anh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ecdc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nhanh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Pereira kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 ch\u1eadm. Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 22, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t Pereira x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPereira mang l\u1ea1i m\u00e0u s\u1eafc m\u1edbi cho M.U. Su\u1ed1t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian Pereira ch\u01a1i cho Valencia d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, Mourinho lu\u00f4n nh\u1eafn tin h\u1ecfi th\u0103m c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, &ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&rdquo; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ef1c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng gi\u00e0u tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng, Pereira ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t &ldquo;Michael Carrick m\u1edbi&rdquo; c\u1ee7a M.U. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:&#xA; solid black .5pt;mso-border-themecolor:text1;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:&#xA; 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"1\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes\">\r\n            <td style=\"border:solid black 1.0pt;mso-border-themecolor:text1;&#xA;  mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;mso-border-themecolor:text1;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\" valign=\"top\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:&#xA;  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 Andreas   Pereira:</strong></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:&#xA;  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><em>T\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7: </em>Andreas Hugo   Hoelgebaum Pereira</p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:&#xA;  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><em>Ng\u00e0y sinh: </em>1/1/1996</p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:&#xA;  .0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><em>N\u01a1i sinh: </em>Duffel, B\u1ec9</p>\r\n            <p cla